quran[25]{c,v,t,f}:
  79,43,"Mmwe nganinkola umanyilisi wanti nikujitomeka."
  79,44,"Kwa Ambuje ŵenupe (Allah) ni kuchipelela kwakwe (kwa umanyilisi wa Kiyama)."
  79,45,"Mmwe masengo genu ni kwaatetela ŵaakujijogopa (Kiyamajo)."
  80,40,"Sano ngope sine lyele lisikulyo sichipakala luwundu."
  80,41,"Sichiŵa siunichilidwe ni chipi."
  80,42,"Ŵanganyao ni ŵali achimakafili ŵakusakasya nnope."
  83,28,"Jwalakwejo ni tutumule jwachakamweje (ŵandu) ŵakuŵandichisyidwa (kwa Allah)."
  83,29,"Chisimu (ku duniya) ŵandu ŵaŵanneŵele (Allah) ŵaliji nkwaseka ŵandu ŵakulupilila."
  83,30,"Mwanti ndema jaŵaliji nkupita (ŵakulupililao) paali ŵanganyao ŵaliji nkukupililana meso (mwakuchembulusya)."
  84,25,"Ikaŵeje aŵala ŵaakulupilile ni kutendaga yambone, akwete kupata ŵanganyao malipilo gangamala."
  85,22,"(Jilembedwe) mu Ubawo Wagosedwa."
  86,16,"None ni ngwauchisya malindi (gaogo pangaapa ilagasyo chitema kuti alilechelele)."
  86,17,"Basi, mwalechelesyani achimakafili, mwalechelelani panandipe (chaiwone)."
  87,13,"Soni ngachija kumpata chiwa mwalakwemo, nambo soni ngaaja kuŵa ni umi (wambone)."
  87,14,"Pamasile paapundile mundu jwaliswejesye (ntima wakwe)."
  87,15,"Ni akuŵa ali nkulikumbuchila Lina lya Ambujegwe (pakulikolanga) aku achiswaliji."
  88,10,"Ku Mbepo Japenani."
  88,11,"Ngasisija kupikana kwalakweko yangali mate."
  88,12,"Kweleko kwana tutumule jwakujilimaga."
  89,7,"Ŵa ku Irama; achalewulewu mpela misaati?"
  89,8,"Ŵanganagumbidweje ŵane ŵanti chisawu ŵanganyao mu ilambo (ine)?"
  89,9,"Ni ŵanya Asamuda ŵaŵaliji nkusokola maganga pachiŵata (chakuŵilanjikwa Wadi Qura kuŵa majumba gao)?"
  90,1,"Nguulumbila awu musi (wa Maaka)."
  90,2,"Soni mmwe (Muhammadi ﷺ) tinchiŵa ŵakundisyidwa (kuputa ngondo) mu wele musiwu."
  90,3,"Ni ngullumbila soni nangolo ni uŵelesi wajuŵeleche."